<emphasis bold="true" box="[1995,2167,1801,1826]" pageId="209" pageNumber="488">Distribution.</emphasis>
E Brazilian Amazon Basin, S of Amazon River, from the W bank of the Tapajos River E to Maranhao and S to Mato Grosso states.
</paragraph>
</caption>
